    {
      "id": "footer",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 600,
      "y": 1850,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 18,
      "strokeColor": "#adb5bd",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "内容源自《品牌全案策略指南2.0》第 2.6 节 创作品牌故事 + 第 2.1 节 创始人IP建设",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.830Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.830Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "ip1-bg",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 145,
      "y": 1162,
      "width": 910,
      "height": 115,
      "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa",
      "strokeColor": "#dee2e6",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.828Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.828Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "ip1-tag",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 205,
      "y": 1173,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 26,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "有 种  —  价值观  ·  忠诚度的入口",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.828Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.828Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "ip1-body",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 160,
      "y": 1208,
      "width": 880,
      "height": 60,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "敢不敢站一个明确的立场？\"用户买的不是你做了什么，而是你为什么而做。\"\n鲜明行业立场 → 筛选同频者。用户共情 → 品牌\"走下神坛\"。—— 核心关键词：价值观。\n《指南2.0》：\"针对行业热点或乱象，输出不容置喙的观点。明确表达你'坚守什么'以及'拒绝什么'。\"",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.828Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.828Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "ip2-bg",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 145,
      "y": 1290,
      "width": 910,
      "height": 100,
      "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa",
      "strokeColor": "#dee2e6",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.828Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.828Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "ip2-tag",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 205,
      "y": 1301,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 26,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "有 料  —  专业度  ·  竞争的护城河",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.829Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.829Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "ip2-body",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 160,
      "y": 1336,
      "width": 880,
      "height": 48,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "有没有行业真相可以讲？核心关键词：专业度。知识金字塔比例 → 30% 基础常识（降低门槛）+ 50% 实战技巧（展示专家感）+ 20% 独家方法论（建立不可替代性）。\n《指南2.0》：\"持续输出对行业趋势、消费者需求及宏观环境的深度洞察。你的认知深度直接决定了品牌的溢价能力。\"",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.829Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.829Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "ip3-bg",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 145,
      "y": 1403,
      "width": 910,
      "height": 100,
      "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa",
      "strokeColor": "#dee2e6",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.829Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.829Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "ip3-tag",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 205,
      "y": 1414,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 26,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "有 趣  —  亲和力  ·  认知的破冰船",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.829Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.829Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "ip3-body",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 160,
      "y": 1448,
      "width": 880,
      "height": 48,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "敢不敢亮出\"不完美的真实\"？核心关键词：亲和力。核心禁忌：严格避免\"摆拍感\"，越是随性、自然的记录越能赢得信任。让冰冷的 CEO 头衔变成鲜活、可触摸的朋友。\n《指南2.0》：\"捕捉创业过程中的非高光时刻，突出'不完美的真实'。\"",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.829Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.829Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
