      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.803Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.803Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "p3-tag",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 205,
      "y": 857,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 26,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "承 诺  My Promise",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.803Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.803Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "p3-body",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 160,
      "y": 895,
      "width": 880,
      "height": 60,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "《指南2.0》：\"把品牌故事与用户的利益点强绑定，用户才会觉得'这个品牌和我有关'。\"\n不说\"我们会继续努力\"，说\"你撕开包装袋那一刻，闻到的只能是食材本身的味道。\"\n案例·深夜小粥铺：\"想让每个加班到深夜的人，能喝上一碗热乎、干净、刚好够吃的粥——就像家里留的那碗。\"",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.803Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.803Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "ip-quote",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 180,
      "y": 1072,
      "width": 840,
      "height": 34,
      "backgroundColor": "#f1f3f5",
      "strokeColor": "#343a40",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 0,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.827Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.827Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "ip-quote-t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 200,
      "y": 1077,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 22,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "📖 《指南2.0》原话：\"初创品牌，老板就是品牌总监和代言人。\"",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.828Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.828Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "ip-body",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 145,
      "y": 1116,
      "width": 910,
      "height": 36,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "《指南2.0》提出\"一体两面\"：创始人既是一个真实的人，也是品牌资产最鲜活的组成部分。不是你\"选择\"做不做 IP — 你没有预算请代言人，没有团队做品牌，你就是品牌。你的脸、声音、态度，是用户唯一能感受到的触点。",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.828Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.828Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "ip-lei",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 145,
      "y": 1514,
      "width": 910,
      "height": 22,
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "strokeColor": "#ffffff",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.829Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.829Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "ip-lei-t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 160,
      "y": 1514,
      "width": 880,
      "height": 44,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "雷军案例（《指南2.0》深度拆解）：\"为发烧而生\"（有种） + 年度演讲发布行业趋势（有料） + \"Are you OK\"自黑接梗、直播间互动（有趣）\n📖 《指南2.0》金句：\"雷军 IP 的威力，在于他将'创始人的真实人格'变成了'品牌最坚实的护城河'。\"",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.829Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.829Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "cta-bg",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 200,
      "y": 1740,
