      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "h-t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 145,
      "y": 152,
      "width": 700,
      "height": 24,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "🎣  钩子：你的品牌介绍是不是也写成这样？",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.797Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.797Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "h-body",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 145,
      "y": 184,
      "width": 910,
      "height": 64,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "\"我们甄选全球优质原料，采用领先工艺，重新定义行业标准……\"\n满怀信心发出去 → 没人转发、没人问\"在哪买\"、连你妈都没点赞。\n👉 《指南2.0》原话：\"这些文字像一套冰冷的盔甲，不仅没能吸引用户，反而把他们推得更远。\"",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.797Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.797Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "c-bg",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 285,
      "width": 960,
      "height": 168,
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "strokeColor": "#dee2e6",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.798Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.798Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "c-bar",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 285,
      "width": 4,
      "height": 168,
      "backgroundColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.798Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.798Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "c-t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 145,
      "y": 293,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 24,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "💡  核心观点：品牌故事的目的不是「装强」，是「赢信」",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.798Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.798Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "c-body",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 145,
      "y": 326,
      "width": 910,
      "height": 72,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "初创品牌要什么没什么 — 没大厂资历、没漂亮背书、没几千家门店。拼命堆形容词想让自己\"够格\"？搞反了。\n大品牌靠规模建立信任，你手里只有一张牌：真实。真实到笨拙、粗糙、不够精致 → 反而让用户觉得\"这个人是真的\"。\n完美的叙事让人免疫，笨拙的真实让人放下戒备。",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.798Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.798Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "c-quote",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 180,
      "y": 406,
      "width": 840,
      "height": 36,
      "backgroundColor": "#f1f3f5",
      "strokeColor": "#343a40",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 0,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.800Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.800Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "c-quote-t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 200,
      "y": 411,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 24,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "📖 《指南2.0》金句：\"创始人的'精神原力'是品牌竞争的终极护城河。\"",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.800Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.800Z",
      "version": 1
    },
