      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "e-t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 145,
      "y": 1581,
      "width": 700,
      "height": 24,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "🏁  一句话总结",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.830Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.830Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "e-body",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 145,
      "y": 1614,
      "width": 910,
      "height": 64,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "讲故事的品牌 vs 不会讲故事的品牌，差别不在文笔 — 在于用户看完是说\n\"哦，又是一家新公司\" 还是 \"对，我也遇到过。\"\n那个\"对，我也遇到过\"的瞬间 = 品牌最深的护城河。竞品可以抄产品、定价、包装，但抄不走你的故事。因为它只从你身上长出来。",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.830Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.830Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "e-quote",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 145,
      "y": 1688,
      "width": 910,
      "height": 24,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "📖 《指南2.0》结尾：\"你是否已经做好了准备……将内心最真实的脆弱与强悍转化为公众的力量，从而赢得这个时代最稀缺的资产——信任。\"",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.830Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-13T07:49:44.830Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "c1-header",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1860,
      "y": 96,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 44,
      "backgroundColor": "#1971c2",
